Write a simple game using any game framework (e.g PyGame, Arcade (Python), or Godot). The following 5 things must be done:

The game must display a background

The game must have at least 1 un-movable object

The game must have at least 1 moveable object

The game must include collisions of at least 2 objects

The game must take user input from the keyboard or mouse

Stretch Challenges (select one):

Allow the user to save and load the game.

Add music or sound effects to the game.

Provide levels in your game that change the difficulty of the game.
